quran[8]{c,v,t,f}:
  43,88,"Soni uŵechete wakwe (Muhammadi ﷺ ndaŵi ni katema ukuŵa wanti): “E Ambuje ŵangu! Chisimu ŵanganyaŵa ni ŵandu ŵangaakukulupilila (kwali ndende nao chichi)!”"
  43,89,"Basi mwalekani, ni m’becheteje (maloŵe ga) ntendele. Basi sampano tayimanye (yakuyichisya ya ukafili wao). ",footnotes:1:Chilamusi cha aji Ȃyaji chafutidwe pakutuluka Ȃya ja (9:5) jakundisya kumenyana nao ngondo.
  50,13,"Ni achina Adi, Firiauna ni achalongo achimijakwe Lutwi."
  50,14,"Ni akutama nyyitekete (ŵandu ŵa Shuaibu), ni ŵandu ŵa Tubba‘i (ŵa ku Yemeni), ŵaliose mwa jamanjao ŵaakaaniile Achimitenga, basi ni chasimichiche chitetelo Changu (pa ŵanganyao)."
  50,15,"Ana ni twapesile ni gumba kwandanda? (Ngwamba), nambo ŵanganyao ali mu kaichila ya gumba kwasambano."
  51,7,"Ngulilumbila liwunde lyalikwete kagumbidwe kambone."
  51,8,"Chisimu ŵanganyammwe n’di pa maloŵe gakutindana (gakwamba Qur’an ni Muhammadi ﷺ)."
  51,9,"Akugalawusyidwa ni galakwego (kuleka kujikulupilila Qur’an ni Muhammadi ﷺ) jwagalawusyidwe (kuleka chikulupi cha Tauhidi)."